# Prompt: Implement Complete Utility Tools Suite for phung.work
## Objective
Build a modern, browser-first **Utility Tools** module for **phung.work** that provides fast, privacy-friendly everyday utilities comparable to DevToys, DevUtils, TinyWow, Browserling, and other professional online tool collections.
The implementation must integrate seamlessly with the existing architecture and design system of phung.work.
---
# Core Principles
* Everything runs locally in the browser.
* No backend.
* No API calls.
* User data never leaves the browser.
* Fast and lightweight.
* Mobile responsive.
* Desktop optimized.
* Dark mode support.
* Accessible (WCAG AA).
* Modular architecture.
* Lazy loading.
* Code splitting.
* Reusable components.
* TypeScript-first implementation.
Do not modify the current routing or application architecture unless absolutely necessary.
